name: testThisProjectIsParameterizedOptionsCollectToList
description: Verification of presence parameters for MultiConfiguration Project on GitHub
descriptionHtml: Verification of presence parameters for MultiConfiguration Project on GitHub

testStage.description: Verification of presence parameters for MultiConfiguration Project on GitHub

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Configure' button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Get all options of Add parameter drop-down menu
Logout from instance http://localhost:8081/
